===Pronunciation===
כּתּנת  -  כּתנת / kethôneth  kûttôneth / keth-o'-neth, koot-to'-neth

===Etymology===
From an unused root meaning to cover (compare H3802); 

===Noun===
'''כּתּנת'''

# A shirt: - [[coat]], garment, robe.

